<title>NEARER MY GOD TO THEE!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na kawm ei naihsak in aw ka Pathien,
 Kross gikpuo himah leng kei ei phawng ding;
 Ka la hizing ina.

[V2]
 Na kawm ei naihsak in (2)
 Aw ka Pathien.

[V3]
 2. Vakvai banga umin, ni a tumin,
 Thimna'n kei ei bawma, suongah ka chawl;
 Mahleh ka manglam in.

[V4]
 3. Ka lampi kilang hen, van lampi chuh!
 Ka kawma Na sawl cheng, lungsietna ziek;
 Angelte'n ei hilh ding.

[V5]
 4. Ka thawh tieng lungthim nuomin ka hun pak,
 Ka lungkhamna ziekin, Bethel sa'ng ka;
 Ka lungkhamna ziekin.
 5. Kipahna tha zakin, Vanah leng leng,
 Ni, tha, aksi khel chunglam ah leng ka;
 Ka la hi zing ina.</lyrics>
</song>